"""
auction_com.py — Ingest Auction.com leads.

COMPLIANCE NOTE:
  Auction.com requires login / uses bot protection for most search pages.
  This module DOES NOT scrape or bypass any authentication or bot protection.
  
  Instead it:
    1. Reads a manually exported CSV from the `uploads/` folder (primary path).
    2. Attempts to read the publicly visible, non-gated search results page as a
       secondary source — but ONLY if robots.txt permits and no bot protection
       is detected. If blocked, it logs clearly and exits gracefully.
    3. Processes and normalises all fields into the standard AuctionRecord model.

  To use: log in to Auction.com, apply your filters, click "Export" / "Download"
  and save the CSV into the `uploads/` folder. The system will auto-detect it.
"""
